{"id":563490,"date":[{"year":1977,"month":10,"day":23}],"page":"2","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"谚语","genre":"","count":"122","ytitle":"","mtitle":"谚语","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"*要想了解自己，最好问问别人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"*真正的聋子是那些不听劝告的人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"*人到事中迷，就怕没人提。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"*要打当面锣，莫敲背后鼓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"*谦虚的人常思己过，骄傲的人只议人非。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"*有错认错，不可说谎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"*荷叶包不住刺菱，缺点瞒不住别人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"*承认错误就等于改正了一半。"}]}